WEBVTT

00:00.050 --> 00:06.206
Skilled craftsmen and tradespeople and factory workers have seen the jobs they loved...

00:06.572 --> 00:10.919
...shipped thousands and thousands of miles away.

00:11.663 --> 00:18.735
Many Pennsylvania towns once thriving and humming are now in a state of total disrepair.

00:19.315 --> 00:25.261
This wave of globalization has wiped out totally our middle class.

00:25.708 --> 00:28.234
It doesn't have to be this way.

00:28.507 --> 00:32.977
We can turn it around, and we can turn it around fast.

00:36.082 --> 00:38.139
But if we're going to deliver real change,...

00:38.224 --> 00:41.715
...we're going to have to reject the campaign of fear and intimidation,...

00:42.047 --> 00:48.622
...being pursued by powerful corporations, media elites, and political dynasties.

00:49.048 --> 00:54.725
The people who rigged the system for their benefit will do anything and say anything...

00:55.119 --> 00:59.186
...to keep things exactly the way they are.

